Arch config script
==================
Installs all utility programs you'll need with my config


Usage
--------
When logged in as root run:

    git clone https://software.raygarner.co.uk/arch_config
    cd arch_config
    ./adduser <username>

Then logout and login as <username> and run

    git clone https://software.raygarner.co.uk/arch_config
    cd arch_config

Make sure to edit the variables in 'setup' to match your username, email and real name then run

    ./setup

